					<![CDATA[
						 <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>Wow! Because of course you are, you raging slutbag.</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <p>This is a collaboration between me and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549483723" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span></p> <p>A long ass time ago, seagull PMed me asking if I wanted to collab with them on a bowl of flies straight out of r/niceguys. I thought the idea was hilarious, so I took up the offer. After several different revisions, this is the result. Hope y'all enjoy it, and thanks to r/niceguys and r/nicegirls for inspiration.</p> <p>Thanks to everyone to who looked at this in discord, really means a lot.</p> 
				 	]]>
